{
  "stem": "10359.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You don't know what will happen tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You-- you're not optimistic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You're not pessimistic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You just work from minute to minute hoping for nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You don't even know what to hope for.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because we didn't know if the war was going good or bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't have any newspapers or radio.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "For a year and a half, we were completely isolated without any human contact, so to say, except my-- with Dorothy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And nobody to talk to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are now in 1942 after we escaped from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, when we escaped--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the third ghetto, the third--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Massacre, third Aktion.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, when they surrounded that ghetto, I already had papers made out for me and Dorothy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to-- now, what I did, I established good communication with some policemen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I drank with them, just in case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is Mark Grinims.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, this was before, before the thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was still while I was between my home and ghetto, back and forth, after the second Aktion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So still Jews remained.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "About 3,000 Jews remained in ghetto in the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I established some type of-- just in case.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I tried to be pally with them, you know, drink with them, talk to them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came to my house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I gave him some soap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I gave him this and that, so in case of something, to let me know what happens.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now when we-- when they surrounded the ghetto, I saw one of the policemen that I just drank last night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I asked him to let me out to Dorothy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he says, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'll let you out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I wouldn't let her out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, forget it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to another guy that I maybe drank two weeks ago.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I gave him five gold pieces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, let me out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how we escaped from the-- from the third Aktion together to the-- to certain, you know, household areas from people who lived around the area.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They noticed us, and that's why they squealed at night that we couldn't stay in that little room that her friends kept her.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to escape to another guy that I established good communication.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I slept for three or four months on the beets and potatoes in a subbasement and ate only once, probably [NON-ENGLISH] once a day--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--dumplings with milk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after a while, he couldn't-- no, I had to pay him too, naturally, with gold and diamonds and all that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after a while, he couldn't keep us because somebody squealed that we are talking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then that he remained with that woman, we went back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went to some other man that I exchanged goods-- eggs, butter, and everything-- someplace 30-- about four or five miles from Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had a big, big farm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he also had a big-- he had a big farm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he had a son and a daughter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had some big plans when it comes to his daughter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when I came to hide out, he wanted to hide me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But once he saw Dorothy, even though I told him it was my cousin, he didn't believe me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he says, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can't keep you both.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had to leave again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had some big plans then, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's why we back-- back to the woman that Dorothy told you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then-- but she couldn't keep us both.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She says, maybe for a while I'll keep you, but I can't keep two people even though I paid her too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I went out to another place that I knew some girl from, from school yet, you know, I was dating her for a while or something.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought maybe they'll help me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They helped me a little bit for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But again, they told me they can't hold me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All three of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All three.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first one, they only took the old people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told you, the sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The second one, they took all the young people, and I got away because I told them I'm a carpenter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The third one in ghetto, we just plainly escaped because we had-- I, I, I paid gold the policemen, and we had the false papers made up.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, all three of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Had to go--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no only two of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The third one was surrounded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We escaped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But only the two we had to go through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Left anything out?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
